<p>The <code>nbsp</code> function replaces spaces with <code>&amp;nbsp;</code> (non-breaking spaces).</p>

<h2>Basic Usage</h2>
<pre>{open}'hello world' | nbsp{close}</pre>
<p>Result: {'hello world' | nbsp}</p>

<h2>Prevent Line Breaks</h2>
<pre>{open}'John Doe' | nbsp{close}</pre>
<p>Won't break: {'John Doe' | nbsp}</p>

<pre>{open}'New York' | nbsp{close}</pre>
<p>City name: {'New York' | nbsp}</p>

<h2>Chained Examples</h2>
<pre>{open}'  multiple spaces  ' | trim | white | nbsp{close}</pre>
<p>Cleaned with nbsp: {'  multiple spaces  ' | trim | white | nbsp}</p>

<h2>Phone Numbers</h2>
<pre>{open}'555 123 4567' | nbsp{close}</pre>
<p>No break: {'555 123 4567' | nbsp}</p>

<h2>With Users</h2>
<pre>{open}users{close}
  {open}$name | nbsp{close}
{open}/users{close}</pre>
<p>Names that won't break:</p>
{users}
  [{$name | nbsp}]<br>
{/users}
